title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Sep 29 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Sep 29 2022
description:
Biden addresses nation on Hurricane, warns oil companies not to raise gas prices. Biden's "Where's Jackie?" moment shocks the White House press corps. Kamala Harris goes to the DMZ, praises the wrong side. Harris could be the reason deteriorating Biden has to run again. Rob Gaudet of the Cajun Navy joins us from devastated Fort Myers. Go to Cajunrelief.org to help them help victims of Hurricane Ian. Joe Concha, media and politics columnist at The Hill, a FOX News contributor, and author of the new book: COME ON, MAN!: The Truth About Joe Biden's Terrible, Horrible, No-Good, Very Bad Presidency, joins Clay and Buck in-studio in New York City.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
